  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*:  `/send` cards (messages) appear too close to screen edges on iPhone 5S\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nCard should take less space on small screens\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/31998087-22e35c68-b997-11e7-881a-e18879322f96.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- As A: Create 1x1 chat or group chat with a contact (B) who runs app on small screen (5S for example)\r\n- As A: Send transaction with 8 or more digits after comma\r\n- As B: open chat and pay attention to `/send` cards \r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: `0.9.12` release build 0.9.11d314-1557.314\r\n* Operating System: iOS",
